            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Esther.8:1-10:3",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EEsther%208%3A1-10%3A3%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_8_1%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEsther%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Decree%20to%20Help%20the%20Jews%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EOn%20that%20same%20day%20King%20Xerxes%20gave%20the%20property%20of%20Haman%2C%20the%20enemy%20of%20the%20Jews%2C%20to%20Queen%20Esther.%20Then%20Mordecai%20was%20brought%20before%20the%20king%2C%20for%20Esther%20had%20told%20the%20king%20how%20they%20were%20related.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_8_2%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%20took%20off%20his%20signet%20ring%26%23x2014%3Bwhich%20he%20had%20taken%20back%20from%20Haman%26%23x2014%3Band%20gave%20it%20to%20Mordecai.%20And%20Esther%20appointed%20Mordecai%20to%20be%20in%20charge%20of%20Haman%26%23x2019%3Bs%20property.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_8_3%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Esther%20went%20again%20before%20the%20king%2C%20falling%20down%20at%20his%20feet%20and%20begging%20him%20with%20tears%20to%20stop%20the%20evil%20plot%20devised%20by%20Haman%20the%20Agagite%20against%20the%20Jews.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_8_4%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EAgain%20the%20king%20held%20out%20the%20gold%20scepter%20to%20Esther.%20So%20she%20rose%20and%20stood%20before%20him.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_8_5%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EEsther%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BIf%20it%20please%20the%20king%2C%20and%20if%20I%20have%20found%20favor%20with%20him%2C%20and%20if%20he%20thinks%20it%20is%20right%2C%20and%20if%20I%20am%20pleasing%20to%20him%2C%20let%20there%20be%20a%20decree%20that%20reverses%20the%20orders%20of%20Haman%20son%20of%20Hammedatha%20the%20Agagite%2C%20who%20ordered%20that%20Jews%20throughout%20all%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20provinces%20should%20be%20destroyed.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_8_6%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20how%20can%20I%20endure%20to%20see%20my%20people%20and%20my%20family%20slaughtered%20and%20destroyed%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_8_7%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20King%20Xerxes%20said%20to%20Queen%20Esther%20and%20Mordecai%20the%20Jew%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20have%20given%20Esther%20the%20property%20of%20Haman%2C%20and%20he%20has%20been%20impaled%20on%20a%20pole%20because%20he%20tried%20to%20destroy%20the%20Jews.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_8_8%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20go%20ahead%20and%20send%20a%20message%20to%20the%20Jews%20in%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20name%2C%20telling%20them%20whatever%20you%20want%2C%20and%20seal%20it%20with%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20signet%20ring.%20But%20remember%20that%20whatever%20has%20already%20been%20written%20in%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20name%20and%20sealed%20with%20his%20signet%20ring%20can%20never%20be%20revoked.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_8_9%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20on%20June%26%23xA0%3B25%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A9a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eon%20the%20twenty-third%20day%20of%20the%20third%20month%2C%20the%20month%20of%20Sivan%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20ancient%20Hebrew%20lunar%20calendar.%20This%20day%20was%20June%26%23xA0%3B25%2C%20474%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3Eb.c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3B%20also%20see%20note%20on%202%3A16.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20secretaries%20were%20summoned%2C%20and%20a%20decree%20was%20written%20exactly%20as%20Mordecai%20dictated.%20It%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20Jews%20and%20to%20the%20highest%20officers%2C%20the%20governors%2C%20and%20the%20nobles%20of%20all%20the%20127%26%23xA0%3Bprovinces%20stretching%20from%20India%20to%20Ethiopia.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A9b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eto%20Cush.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20decree%20was%20written%20in%20the%20scripts%20and%20languages%20of%20all%20the%20peoples%20of%20the%20empire%2C%20including%20that%20of%20the%20Jews.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_8_10%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20decree%20was%20written%20in%20the%20name%20of%20King%20Xerxes%20and%20sealed%20with%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20signet%20ring.%20Mordecai%20sent%20the%20dispatches%20by%20swift%20messengers%2C%20who%20rode%20fast%20horses%20especially%20bred%20for%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20service.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_8_11%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20decree%20gave%20the%20Jews%20in%20every%20city%20authority%20to%20unite%20to%20defend%20their%20lives.%20They%20were%20allowed%20to%20kill%2C%20slaughter%2C%20and%20annihilate%20anyone%20of%20any%20nationality%20or%20province%20who%20might%20attack%20them%20or%20their%20children%20and%20wives%2C%20and%20to%20take%20the%20property%20of%20their%20enemies.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_8_12%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20day%20chosen%20for%20this%20event%20throughout%20all%20the%20provinces%20of%20King%20Xerxes%20was%20March%26%23xA0%3B7%20of%20the%20next%20year.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A12%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20thirteenth%20day%20of%20the%20twelfth%20month%2C%20the%20month%20of%20Adar%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20ancient%20Hebrew%20lunar%20calendar.%20The%20date%20selected%20was%20March%26%23xA0%3B7%2C%20473%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3Eb.c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3B%20also%20see%20note%20on%202%3A16.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_8_13%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EA%20copy%20of%20this%20decree%20was%20to%20be%20issued%20as%20law%20in%20every%20province%20and%20proclaimed%20to%20all%20peoples%2C%20so%20that%20the%20Jews%20would%20be%20ready%20to%20take%20revenge%20on%20their%20enemies%20on%20the%20appointed%20day.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_8_14%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20urged%20on%20by%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20command%2C%20the%20messengers%20rode%20out%20swiftly%20on%20fast%20horses%20bred%20for%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20service.%20The%20same%20decree%20was%20also%20proclaimed%20in%20the%20fortress%20of%20Susa.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_8_15%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Mordecai%20left%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20presence%2C%20wearing%20the%20royal%20robe%20of%20blue%20and%20white%2C%20the%20great%20crown%20of%20gold%2C%20and%20an%20outer%20cloak%20of%20fine%20linen%20and%20purple.%20And%20the%20people%20of%20Susa%20celebrated%20the%20new%20decree.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_8_16%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20Jews%20were%20filled%20with%20joy%20and%20gladness%20and%20were%20honored%20everywhere.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_8_17%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20every%20province%20and%20city%2C%20wherever%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20decree%20arrived%2C%20the%20Jews%20rejoiced%20and%20had%20a%20great%20celebration%20and%20declared%20a%20public%20festival%20and%20holiday.%20And%20many%20of%20the%20people%20of%20the%20land%20became%20Jews%20themselves%2C%20for%20they%20feared%20what%20the%20Jews%20might%20do%20to%20them.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_9_1%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEsther%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Victory%20of%20the%20Jews%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20on%20March%26%23xA0%3B7%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eon%20the%20thirteenth%20day%20of%20the%20twelfth%20mon