f%20they%20have%20done%20that%20here%2C%20what%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20provinces%3F%20But%20now%2C%20what%20more%20do%20you%20want%3F%20It%20will%20be%20granted%20to%20you%3B%20tell%20me%20and%20I%20will%20do%20it.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_9_13%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EEsther%20responded%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BIf%20it%20please%20the%20king%2C%20give%20the%20Jews%20in%20Susa%20permission%20to%20do%20again%20tomorrow%20as%20they%20have%20done%20today%2C%20and%20let%20the%20bodies%20of%20Haman%26%23x2019%3Bs%20ten%20sons%20be%20impaled%20on%20a%20pole.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_9_14%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20king%20agreed%2C%20and%20the%20decree%20was%20announced%20in%20Susa.%20And%20they%20impaled%20the%20bodies%20of%20Haman%26%23x2019%3Bs%20ten%20sons.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_9_15%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20Jews%20at%20Susa%20gathered%20together%20on%20March%26%23xA0%3B8%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A15%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20fourteenth%20day%20of%20the%20month%20of%20Adar%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20ancient%20Hebrew%20lunar%20calendar.%20This%20day%20was%20March%26%23xA0%3B8%2C%20473%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3Eb.c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3B%20also%20see%20note%20on%202%3A16.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20killed%20300%26%23xA0%3Bmore%20men%2C%20and%20again%20they%20took%20no%20plunder.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_9_16%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2216%22